Name: EndZ Village
About the game: Village building game in the age of collapse Simulation of the construction of a village in the Zombie Age, Players must research and develop the village. Add forces Build a strong base to attack many zombies. Resource management in food and construction , The game will continue. And found unexpected events with players Or to send explorers to explore various places To increase the manpower and resources of village. - Simulation of the construction of villages in the Zombie Age - Construction of villages through desperation - Search for resources to build a village - Gene research for population development - Prevent attacks from zombies During the development of the village - Develop weapons to increase attack power and defense Farming is an important part of the game. - Corn wheat farming - Animal husbandry system To produce food - Fishing
